guild.description:
Welcome to +NonPoliticalMemes! The third biggest apolitical meme guild on ruqqus!

Here are some basic rules:

**😴 NO POLITICS** You can have memes talking about political events and having politicians as long as they don't have a political leaning

**💩 NO SHIT MEMES** No facebook tier shit or reddit shit. Also, no moldy memes

**😳 DIRECT IMAGE LINKING ONLY** Use direct image linking, if you don't have enough rep use sites like imgur with a .png, .jpg or a .gif after the url, nobody wants to open stuff in another tab. Video links are an exception to this rule

**👽 FOLLOW RUQQUS TOS** follow pls
Join the +ApoliticalGuildsUnion to find more Apolitical Guilds!
